  <brief_title>Safety/Efficacy of Sitagliptin in Patient w/ Type 2 Diabetes (0431-801)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Double-Blind, Placebo and Active Controlled, Randomized Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of the Addition of Sitagliptin 100 mg Once Daily in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes With Inadequate Glycemic Control on Metformin Monotherapy</official_title>
